494
00:41:07,938 --> 00:41:14,904
<i>Is it not miraculous how one's fortune
can turn so quickly, so completely.</i>

495
00:41:15,196 --> 00:41:18,240
<i>One moment, leaping from
a hotel window, the next</i>

496
00:41:18,324 --> 00:41:22,369
