497
00:41:23,412 --> 00:41:26,665
<i>My only problem is that I
accidentally got hooked on a journal</i>

498
00:41:26,791 --> 00:41:29,626
<i>written in 1849 by a dying
lawyer during the voyage</i>

499
00:41:29,627 --> 00:41:32,339
<i>from the Pacific islands
