if you don't want me to come in?

689
00:56:05,523 --> 00:56:06,607
Because, smarty pants,

690
00:56:06,732 --> 00:56:09,275
the only thing worse than having
you jumping onto my balcony,

691
00:56:09,276 --> 00:56:12,655
