1573
02:29:10,482 --> 02:29:11,483
Home.

1574
02:29:18,532 --> 02:29:20,534
Megan Sixsmith?

1575
02:29:30,962 --> 02:29:32,422
Make them pay.

1576
02:29:36,968 --> 02:29:39,012
You can count on it.

1577
02:29:48,396 --> 02:29:49,522
Thank you.

1578
02:29:53,526 --> 02:29:55,612
My uncle was a scientist,

1579
02:29:55,737 --> 02:29:59,282
