1588
02:30:46,080 --> 02:30:48,624
<i>Watched you for as long as I dared.</i>

1589
02:30:50,793 --> 02:30:55,464
<i>I don't believe it was a fluke
that I saw you first.</i>

1590
02:30:58,577 --> 02:30:59,829
